"(define/IC (USB-Type-C)
  ;; FIXME CAUTION the GND pins (A1 A12 might not be physically connected
  #:ALIAS ([A1 A12 B1 B12 GND]
          [A4 A9 B9 B4 VBUS]
          [A5 CC1]
          [B5 CC2]
          [A6 D+1]
          [B6 D+2]
          [A7 D-1]
          [B7 D-2]

          [A8 SBU1]
          [B8 SBU2])
  #:FP ((fp-usb 'c-female)

        ;; FIXME 4 more pads?
        A1 A2 A3 A4 A5 A6 A7 A8 A9 A10 A11 A12
        B1 B2 B3 B4 B5 B6 B7 B8 B9 B10 B11 B12))"
